              <h3>The Backstory</h3>
              <p>Yo! We’re Bort and Caleb...and we’re excited that you’re checking us out. At one point along this path, we were both simply concerned about getting easier access to fresh herbs to cook with. So we grew our own. Immediately, we noticed the bump in flavor and freshness. We also began to realize that growing your own herbs also has other perks: convenience, less waste, and saving some serious dough at the grocery store (especially if you already opt for organic).</p>
              <p>We found fulfillment in tending to our plants and watching them flourish. We even started to get a little crazy and grew some bizarre, beautiful, and delicious fruit and veggies from around the world. We found a creative outlet in selecting plants that complemented our favorite cooking styles and cocktail recipes. It evokes a honest sense of pride and badassery when you walk out your back door, snip off a couple sprigs of lemon thyme, and use that astounding aroma and flavor to bring out the highest potential in your own inspired culinary creation. We’re hardcode home cooks, cocktail enthusiasts, DC denizens, and big fans of living the Good Life…join us on that journey!</p>
